msgstr "contempt … "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.8"
msgid "macchariyaṃ … "
msgstr "stinginess … "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.9"
msgid "pāpikā issā … "
msgstr "nasty jealousy … "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.10"
msgid "pāpikā icchā abhibhuyya iriyati. "
msgstr "or corrupt wishes master them and keep going. "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.11"
msgid "So evamassa veditabbo: "
msgstr "You should know of them: "

msgctxt "an10.23:7.12"
msgid "‘nāyamāyasmā tathā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ lobho abhibhuyya iriyati; "
msgstr "‘This venerable does not have the understanding that would eliminate greed, so greed masters them and keeps going. "

