msgid "‘tathā ayamāyasmā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ lobho nābhibhuyya iriyati; "
msgstr "‘This venerable has the understanding that eliminates greed, so greed doesn’t master them and keep going. "

